190
00:06:56,583 --> 00:06:58,585
WELL, SOMEONE DID.

191
00:06:59,586 --> 00:07:00,879
SO...

192
00:07:00,963 --> 00:07:02,256
DO YOU WANNA SPEND
SOME TIME WITH ME?

193
00:07:02,339 --> 00:07:04,174
