194
00:07:04,258 --> 00:07:06,134
BUT I CAN'T LEAVE THE STORE.

195
00:07:06,218 --> 00:07:07,469
OH, OF COURSE, WORK.

196
00:07:07,553 --> 00:07:09,221
GOD, I'M SO STUPID.

197
00:07:09,304 --> 00:07:11,640
BUT WE CAN HAVE IT HERE.

198
00:07:11,723 --> 00:07:13,767
ELISE:
SEE YA, CHARLIE.

199
00:07:13,851 --> 00:07:15,018
